Package: tidyversindonesia
Type: Package
Title: A Learning Bridge to the Tidyverse for Indonesia
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yandi", "Andiyana", 
           email = "yandi.andiyana@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Provides Tidyverse functions with Indonesian-language names to help learners 
    in Indonesia grasp data science concepts more intuitively. It serves as an 
    educational bridge built upon the Tidyverse data-science workflow 
    (import, tidy, transform, visualize, model, and communicate). Once mastered, 
    users can easily transition to the original Tidyverse packages.
